olor: rgb(189, 237, 255)\"><strong>S</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(197, 233, 249)\"><strong>C</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 229, 243)\"><strong>E</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 225, 237)\"><strong>N</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 231)\"><strong>A</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 217, 225)\"><strong>R</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 213, 219)\"><strong>I</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 209, 213)\"><strong>O</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 237, 255)\"><strong>▸ Location </strong>:</span> The headquarters of The Corvus Syndicate,</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 237, 255)\"><strong>▸ Time </strong>:</span> Morning</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 237, 255)\"><strong>▸ Context </strong>:</span> Viktor knew what he had to do... He knew the syndicate had to come down. It all started with <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">the Corvus Syndicate. His father was dead. Now all that was left Leksei. Take out the head before the rest realize. Let the empire rot from within. No syndicate. No more sleepless nights. But when he woke up...the papers, the details...gone. <strong><em>What if someone knew?</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 237, 255)\"><strong>▸ Role </strong>: </span>A part of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">the Corvus Syndicate, your role position is up to you. You found evidence that Viktor plans to betray and Kill Leksei.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 351px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_e66d89cd-512b-48e9-87a3-d12f9e1c5b85.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 237, 255)\"><strong>Corvus Syndicate Members:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><strong>Mikhail: <em